text: Sandefjord is a city and municipality in Vestfold county, Norway. In 2022, 64,943 people lived there. On 1 January 2017, the former municipalities of Andebu and Stokke were merged into Sandefjord. ==Related pages== *List of mayors in Norway that are elected until 2027 == Other websites == * Official website Category:Cities in Norway Category:Municipalities of Vestfold
